### Create Wallet 1 (USD)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "currency": "USD"
}

> {% client.global.set("wallet1Id", response.body.id); %}

### Create Wallet 2 (USD)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "currency": "USD"
}

> {% client.global.set("wallet2Id", response.body.id); %}

### Deposit $1000 to Wallet 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/wallets/{{wallet1Id}}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amountMinorUnits": 100000,
  "idempotencyKey": "deposit-{{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Initial deposit"
}

### Transfer $300 from Wallet 1 to Wallet 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/wallets/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromWalletId": "{{wallet1Id}}",
  "toWalletId": "{{wallet2Id}}",
  "amountMinorUnits": 30000,
  "idempotencyKey": "transfer-{{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "Test transfer"
}

### Trigger Manual Reconciliation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/reconcile